data.description: *Virtual Tour to view 3D walkthrough. Welcome to this 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom gem nestled in a vibrant community. The entrance greets you with a versatile office & spacious dining room. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the kitchen, breakfast nook, and living room, creating an inviting and functional space. The kitchen boasts sleek stainless steel appliances. The living room features a charming fireplace and a soaring vaulted ceiling. Upstairs, the primary bedroom awaits, complete with an ensuite bath and a generously sized walk-in closet. Two additional bedrooms and another full bath provide comfort and convenience. Plus, there's a versatile loft space awaiting your imagination. Step outside to the delightful sunroom and the fenced backyard. Beyond your new home, the community offers a wealth of amenities, including a pool, fitness center, lake, hiking trails, and more. This home embodies comfort, style, and community living. Offering a $5,000 carpet allowance for buyers! Hurry!
